 <h1>The expression of legal argumentation: Towards a methodology for narrative studies of ‘discourses of subsumption’</h1> 


 
















<ul class="contributors list-unstyled mb-2">

    
            
                
                    
    <li class="contributors-AUTHOR mb-2">
        
