lar?q=Lindell%2C%20B.%201987.%20Sakfr%C3%A5gor%20och%20r%C3%A4ttsfr%C3%A5gor%3A%20en%20studie%20av%20gr%C3%A4nser%2C%20skillnader%20och%20f%C3%B6rh%C3%A5llanden%20mellan%20faktum%20och%20r%C3%A4tt.%20Uppsala%3A%20Iustus." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_ijld-2016-0003_ref_023_w2aab2b8c10b1b7b1ab2ac23Aa"><span class="reference-mixed-citation">MacCormick, N. 1978. Legal reasoning and legal theory. Oxford: Clarendon.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=MacCormick%2C%20N.%201978.%20Legal%20reasoning%20and%20legal%20theory.%20Oxford%3A%20Clarendon." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_ijld-2016-0003_ref_024_w2aab2b8c10b1b7b1ab2ac24Aa"><span class="reference-mixed-citation">Mussawir, E. 2011. Jurisidiction in deleuze: The expression and representation of law. Abingdon: Routledge.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://doi.org/10.4324/9780203829622" class="link link-external doi" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">10.4324/9780203829622</a><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Mussawir%2C%20E.%202011.%20Jurisidiction%20in%20deleuze%3A%20The%20expression%20and%20representation%20of%20law.%20Abingdon%3A%20Routledge." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_ijld-2016-0003_ref_025_w2aab2b8c10b1b7b1ab2ac25Aa"><span class="reference-mixed-citation">Philippoulos-Mihalopoulos, A. 2014. Spatial justice: Body, lawscape, atmosphere (space, materiality and the normative). Abingdon: Routledge.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://doi.org/10.4324/9781315780528" class="link link-external doi" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow"